pacman

Class PacMan

  • java.lang.Object
    • pacman.GameCharacter
      • pacman.PacMan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visited
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MightyPacMan, RegularPacMan, SuperPacMan

    public abstract class PacMan
extends GameCharacter
implements Visited
    Author:
    Tom Leibovich and Roee Shachar 'PacMan' represents the pacman. It contains its unique start position, and the next direction desired by the user. In order to apply the relationships between the various pacman's and monsters, the class implements the Visited interface, which allows a monster to see if it can beat pacman.
